然<br />\n<br />\n至少在生日的日子發覺身邊的不會是最後的。<br />\n<br />\n新一年新開始，開心生活，期待你的 Mr. Right 不是更好嗎？</blockquote><br />\n但我愛佢"},{"pid":"d1371c234daa4b839f9205a10ecdca25a40032b5","tid":253980,"uid":71465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T02:46:30.000Z","msg":"生日快樂<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">該要放下的 就放下吧... <br />\n              痛苦過後 前面仍有一大段路等著你走</span>"},{"pid":"6836e4147e9715f050436f892589b6f2a2ef9983","tid":253980,"uid":105833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T02:55:09.000Z","msg":"我都係今日生日<br />\n生日快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96d50699c47c5d3c0ddb3fb63d27d0f7409350c5","tid":253980,"uid":48366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T03:05:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係今日生日<br />\n生日快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n生日快樂"},{"pid":"79a3e0a45ceac76ca194be3a8fc13ab4b8b7cdc2","tid":253980,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T03:05:59.000Z","msg":"祝你年年都有今日"},{"pid":"cafea8f0ecb0855ba3ad5d4ad966ba71e04c3b62","tid":253980,"uid":48366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T03:07:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>祝你年年都有今日</blockquote><br />\n屌你"},{"pid":"6859dec96f99a9ccd2d2bf312d7989a722068033","tid":253980,"uid":75660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T03:08:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我都係今日生日<br />\n生日快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n生日快樂</blockquote><br />\n生日快樂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好難得今年生日無落雨"},{"pid":"cec7855df314f9fa25d0398c282b4403cc13d583","tid":253980,"uid":105833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T03:20:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我都係今